    <p>A note at the foot of fol. 172 b gives the name of the scribe, <persName ref="">Isaac</persName>: </p>
    <p>
        <quote xml:lang="syr">ܝܫܘܥ ܐܠܗܐ̇ ܚܲܣܐ ܒܛܝܒܘܬܟ܇ ܠܐܝܣܚܩ ܚܛܝܐ̣. ܕܟܬܼܒ ܠܣܒܪܬܟ</quote>
